  "name": "RPlog_Speech_for_the_Students",
  "title": "The Horansi Ambassador's Address",
  "summary": "At Covenant College on New Alderaan, a political symposium gathers students to hear the Horansi ambassador K'tyyri Tarashabi and the Mon Calamari Senator Tokoga speak. K'tyyri, a former N'kosi of Mutanda, delivers a proud and stirring account of her people's caste society, their war against the Empire and Corporate Sector Authority, and her plea for an ally to free her ruined homeworld. As the New Republic officer Rasi reconnects with the medic Myiari and meets the Wookiee cadet Hauwka assigned to his ship, Senator Tokoga takes the podium, only to be seemingly killed by a focused explosive hidden in the lectern. Myiari rushes to stabilize the gravely wounded Senator while Hauwka secures the area, and the wounded man is loaded into an ambulance. Once inside, Rasi reveals the whole attack was a staged ruse: Tokoga is unharmed, and his faked death is a gambit to bait the crime lord Nass into paying the bounty he placed, exposing himself to prosecution. The angry Horansi and the displeased medic reluctantly accept the deception as the ambulance reaches the hospital and the ruse holds.",
